- Reads all lines with `std::getline()`
- Parses each line with `std::stoi()`, `std::stod()` (60M rows)
- ~12.5 seconds of pure I/O and string parsing

**Should be**:
- Use `gendb_dir` to mmap binary `.col` files from `tpch_sf10.gendb/`
- Direct binary array access (no parsing)
- Use zone maps to skip irrelevant blocks
- ~20-30ms execution time

### Critical Fix (MANDATORY)
Switch from CSV parsing to binary columnar storage by mmapping:
- `lineitem_l_shipdate.col` (int32_t, 4 bytes × 60M)
